com.team1389.hardware.inputs.software

Class DigitalIn

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team1389.hardware.inputs.software.DigitalIn

  • public class DigitalIn
extends java.lang.Object
    a boolean input stream. The purpose of this class wrapped around BinaryInput is to make the stream operations chainable (you can call them on a stream instance and they return the same stream instance)
    Author:
    amind
